    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drift City is an Open World Driving Drifting Sim with Deep Car Customization such as Speed, Suspension, different driving system and styles and much more which you can read down below. There are 8 cars that can be unlocked for the Early Access and we will add at least 20 cars to the game. It has 6 different cameras/views to see the car and play. There are also Slow-motion and Nitro for all cars available. It has a mini-map so you can see where you go and what you will face and amazing music that can be muted if you wish. More in detail down below.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras/811652c552dfc78424f3b504bc85fe2a.webp?t=1749806029\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras_big/811652c552dfc78424f3b504bc85fe2a.webp?t=1749806029 width=800 height=9 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>CUSTOMIZATION</u>                                                               </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Suspension</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Front Suspension Spring Force </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Front Suspension Spring Damp </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rear Suspension Spring Force </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rear Suspension Spring Damp </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Front Camber </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rear Camber </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Front Suspension </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rear Suspension</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras/b4c563b2f4f93cd56d0a6ea0aeef88fc.avif?t=1749806029\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras_big/b4c563b2f4f93cd56d0a6ea0aeef88fc.avif?t=1749806029 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras/811652c552dfc78424f3b504bc85fe2a.webp?t=1749806029\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras_big/811652c552dfc78424f3b504bc85fe2a.webp?t=1749806029 width=800 height=9 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>ELECTRONIC SYSTEMS &amp; DRIVING STYLES</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Driving Assistants</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ABS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ESP</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TCS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SH</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Driving Behavior</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simulator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Racing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drift</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Semi Arcade</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras/fe5f663b09bc2e2f5b5824f27c44776b.avif?t=1749806029\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras_big/fe5f663b09bc2e2f5b5824f27c44776b.avif?t=1749806029 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras/0a31d3e8b2b1d2a6c48ea34e239f6fc1.avif?t=1749806029\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras_big/0a31d3e8b2b1d2a6c48ea34e239f6fc1.avif?t=1749806029 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras/811652c552dfc78424f3b504bc85fe2a.webp?t=1749806029\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras_big/811652c552dfc78424f3b504bc85fe2a.webp?t=1749806029 width=800 height=9 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>COLORS</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Headlight Colors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wheel Smoke Colors</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras/bb0783b0851633b840d69db495009bb7.avif?t=1749806029\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras_big/bb0783b0851633b840d69db495009bb7.avif?t=1749806029 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras/811652c552dfc78424f3b504bc85fe2a.webp?t=1749806029\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras_big/811652c552dfc78424f3b504bc85fe2a.webp?t=1749806029 width=800 height=9 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>DRIVING CUSTOMIZATION</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maximum Speed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maximum Brake</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maximum Torque</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turbo</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exhaust Flame</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rev Limiter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto Transmission</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RWD</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FWD</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ADW</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clutch Threshold</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear Shifting Threshold</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras/37e8817843ba04a06357a3e83e0125f3.avif?t=1749806029\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269070/extras_big/37e8817843ba04a06357a3e83e0125f3.avif?t=1749806029 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
